		- volume slider refresh now always correct
		- included load check of old 2.3 100-Pattern mod, blocked
		  (if anyone needs 100Pattern Mode i must include this)
		- rearranged some GFX
		- All code if aviable now in Fast RAM
		- new replay routine from HÍvard Pedersen (PTSupport Arc)
		  included, it seems to be much more stable then the old
		- added some internal code sanity checks


24.02.96 @{fg shine}PT3.31@{fg text}
		- Shifted keymaps in Getlines works again
		- correct gadgets in Disk Format functions
		- removed bug who makes more marked lines in DirWindow
		  then on mouse position if medium are slow enough
		- improved speed of playtime calculation
		- reset the keyboard shortcuts LALT,CTRL etc. now correct
		  in all situations
		- IFF8SVX detection saver


03.03.96 @{fg shine}PT3.32@{fg text}
		- keyboard broker included against deadlocks from Rawkey
		- PED routines overwritten. Now its possible to use samples
		  with real spaces and national font symbols in PLST/PED.
		- PLST double check debugged. Empty strings now compete
