		- correct calls of xpkmaster.library and internal buffer
		  speedup
		- whole PLST overwritten
		- Smart optimations in patternscroll
		  now on test blank A1200 (slowest i can grab here) no more
		  showable delays also in 250 BPM
		- Overwritten onlinehelp
		- drumpad mode works now also on A2000/3000/4000 keyboard
		- mouse problems on some A4000, workaround
		- gadgets are visible are now usuable (eg Help + Edit
Options)
		- Back to the old GFX Design
		- forgot to use the internal keymap if no external is loaded.

